      "is_table_cell": false,
      "table_info": null,
      "style": "Normal"
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "source": "The completely concealed door hinge TE 440 3D comes with the identical milling pattern and familiar appearance of the TE 340 3D but offers significantly more load capacity – without any visual differences.",
      "target": "",
      "status": "untranslated",
      "paragraph_id": 11,
      "document_position": 11,
      "notes": "",
      "modified": false,
      "created_at": "2025-10-12T16:41:13.101212",
      "modified_at": "2025-10-12T16:41:13.101212",
      "is_table_cell": false,
      "table_info": null,
      "style": "Normal"
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "source": "This means that doors weighing up to 100 kg can also be integrated easily and in keeping with the style, such as lighter fire or soundproof doors.",
      "target": "",
      "status": "untranslated",
      "paragraph_id": 12,
      "document_position": 12,
      "notes": "",
      "modified": false,
      "created_at": "2025-10-12T16:41:13.101212",
      "modified_at": "2025-10-12T16:41:13.101212",
      "is_table_cell": false,
      "table_info": null,
      "style": "Normal"
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "source": "But the hinge offers much more than that.",
      "target": "",
      "status": "untranslated",
      "paragraph_id": 13,
      "document_position": 13,
      "notes": "",
      "modified": false,
      "created_at": "2025-10-12T16:41:13.101212",
      "modified_at": "2025-10-12T16:41:13.101212",
      "is_table_cell": false,
      "table_info": null,
      "style": "Normal"
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "source": "TE 440 3D is an addition to our proven product brand TECTUS.",
      "target": "",
      "status": "untranslated",
      "paragraph_id": 14,
      "document_position": 14,
      "notes": "",
      "modified": false,
      "created_at": "2025-10-12T16:41:13.101212",
      "modified_at": "2025-10-12T16:41:13.101212",
      "is_table_cell": false,
      "table_info": null,
      "style": "Normal"
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "source": "With a load capacity of up to 100 kg, it is specifically designed to bridge the gap between the TE 340 3D with load capacity up to 80 kg and the TE 540 3D with load capacity up to 120 kg.",
      "target": "",
      "status": "untranslated",
      "paragraph_id": 15,
      "document_position": 15,
      "notes": "",
      "modified": false,
      "created_at": "2025-10-12T16:41:13.101212",
      "modified_at": "2025-10-12T16:41:13.101212",
      "is_table_cell": false,
      "table_info": null,
      "style": "Normal"
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "source": "The new TE 440 3D achieves a load capacity of up to 100 kg with only two hinges per door.",
      "target": "",
      "status": "untranslated",
      "paragraph_id": 16,
      "document_position": 16,
      "notes": "",
      "modified": false,
      "created_at": "2025-10-12T16:41:13.101212",
      "modified_at": "2025-10-12T16:41:13.101212",
      "is_table_cell": false,
      "table_info": null,
      "style": "Normal"
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "source": "This ensures high efficiency in processing, installation, and performance.",
      "target": "",
      "status": "untranslated",
      "paragraph_id": 17,
      "document_position": 17,
      "notes": "",
      "modified": false,
      "created_at": "2025-10-12T16:41:13.101212",
      "modified_at": "2025-10-12T16:41:13.101212",
      "is_table_cell": false,
      "table_info": null,
      "style": "Normal"
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
